or a high school student. Unlike the chemistry kits that are lacking in necessary materials, this product presents top-notch supplies to start experiments and enough of them to reuse for future experiments. Your child can tackle 333 different experiments with the instructions and materials included in this more advanced chemistry set. The CHEM C3000 is clearly our Top Ten Reviews Gold Award winner for chemistry sets.","Make no mistake: Although this is a chemistry set for kids, it is not for beginners. Some of the experiments can be tricky and potentially dangerous, so you need to impress on your student that it is essential to follow the directions the kit provides for each experiment.","Fortunately, Thames &amp; Kosmos, the chemistry set manufacturer, includes a 176-page experiment manual that explains how the procedures should go. You probably will want to be on hand or have another responsible adult available to observe and possibly assist your budding chemist, no matter how carefully he or she has handled such materials in the past."]},"id":"2873116d-d8d5-4656-84f2-56e42b660605","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Experiments"},"id":"5af470a7-09e3-4d02-b661-c8ea068b51be","type":"heading"},{"data":{"path":"/fo4S7rxL7qM9GVMg3quuD4.jpg","link":{"href":"","rel":null,"target":""},"caption":"","fullscreen":true,"importSrc":"http://www.toptenreviews.com/i/rev/scrn/small/49703-chem-c30002.jpg","src":"https://dev.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/fo4S7rxL7qM9GVMg3quuD4.jpg","credit":"","align":"","id":"fo4S7rxL7qM9GVMg3quuD4","mos":"https://dev.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/fo4S7rxL7qM9GVMg3quuD4.jpg","alt":""},"id":"78629c77-defa-4bd0-8534-32be4e52f6c8","type":"image"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["The CHEM C3000 contains supplies and instructions for 333 different experiments, from the standbys, such as acids and bases, baking soda reactions and chemical identification, to more obscure experiments, such as building a mini fire extinguisher. The experiment list runs the gamut, from mostly entertaining, with magic tricks and colored ink tests, to purely educational, with science kit experiments on elemental properties and chemical identification.","The experiment list in the CHEM C3000 gives an overview of many of the major chemistry principles students learn in high school. Like a chemistry class, the manual for this set moves from general lessons on topics, such as the nature of elements, the behavior of atoms and molecules, and the proper procedures for scientific experimentation, into more advanced lessons demonstrating complex chemical properties, such as combustion, and finally into more real-world applications, such as understanding environmental forces and measuring water quality. Though you might have to buy the chemicals you need for some experiments, this is the most complete chemistry set we reviewed.","While even this complete set cannot take the place of a standard science education, the hands-on experience of conducting experiments cements the lessons learned in the classroom and inspires students to want to learn more.","That said, be aware that the CHEM C3000 set is not a toy anyone can play with carelessly. The experiments in this kit can be dangerous, and you need follow the procedure manual closely. The manufacturer recommends parental supervision and guidance for all experiments involving heat and chemicals. The C3000 kit is designed for more advanced students, so if you are buying this kit for a beginner, you should choose one of the more basic sets, such as the CHEM C500."]},"id":"0e650f3d-d2f9-45e8-86b6-eb85f2cd07d4","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Supplies"},"id":"b6eca003-36f0-461b-b0c2-3ff22a4ee26f","type":"heading"},{"data":{"path":"/nxBQp2dVJpYMQkvbECSAYE.jpg","link":{"href":"","rel":null,"target":""},"caption":"","fullscreen":true,"importSrc":"http://www.toptenreviews.com/i/rev/scrn/small/49703-chem-c30004.jpg","src":"https://dev.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/nxBQp2dVJpYMQkvbECSAYE.jpg","credit":"","align":"","id":"nxBQp2dVJpYMQkvbECSAYE"