onal chemicals that are not included. Most of the chemicals you need will be included, and the rest can be found at a grocery or hardware store, or a science supply store like Best Science Supplies. Even though this could be seen as a drawback of the kit, there are enough experiments included that you can send away for the missing chemicals and have plenty of experiments to keep you busy while you wait for your shipment."]},"id":"396fbd6b-ff47-4a25-b052-5f79624f427c","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Learning Materials"},"id":"b4385360-c55f-4c7a-b2c7-754d0fd68eca","type":"heading"},{"data":{"path":"/PiKgfhFqzVLPFKU4saur3R.jpg","link":{"href":"","rel":null,"target":""},"caption":"The CHEM C3000 is the most advanced kit on our lineup, so the manual is written in a moderately advanced style. Kids who are ready for the C3000 should already be familiar with the scientific method and the rules of proper experimentation, but this information is still included in the manual. The C3000 is better suited to students who have already demonstrated an affinity for science than to students who are struggling to pick up the basic principles.","fullscreen":true,"importSrc":"http://www.toptenreviews.com/i/rev/scrn/small/49703-chem-c30009.jpg","src":"https://dev.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/PiKgfhFqzVLPFKU4saur3R.jpg","credit":"","align":"","id":"PiKgfhFqzVLPFKU4saur3R","mos":"https://dev.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/PiKgfhFqzVLPFKU4saur3R.jpg","alt":""},"id":"36493cb6-474a-45a7-a188-167fb0a5f40b","type":"image"},{"data":{"paragraphs":[" "]},"id":"6f24e29e-073d-4f28-ab9c-7e9fc1900db3","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Summary"},"id":"a7dc0c1a-8a76-441b-85b6-09eac2a570d4","type":"heading"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["The CHEM C3000 tops our list of the best chemistry sets for kids for the sheer volume of experiments you get, as well as the high-quality equipment. The equipment includes glass and metal, not just plastic, so it is durable enough to last through repeated use. While it is not a set for beginner